item.title: CVE-2023-50314|2024-08-14T17:22:31.591Z -- ibm -- websphere%20application%20liberty
item.description: IBM WebSphere Application Server Liberty 17.0.0.3 through 24.0.0.8 could allow an attacker with access to the network to conduct spoofing attacks. An attacker could exploit this vulnerability using a certificate issued by a trusted authority to obtain sensitive information. IBM X-Force ID: 274713.
